                     /note="Phage 186 bacterial attachment site attB,
                     overlapping the 3′ half of the tRNA-Ile gene (preserved on
                     integration). 46 bp shared core (identical to the 186_attP
                     core), read 5′->3′ on the minus strand of NC_000913.3 at
                     the tRNA-Ile locus. NCBI annotates the gene as ileX
                     (b3069); the phage/pOSIP literature names the site ileY
                     (distinct from NCBI ileY b2652 — a nomenclature caveat).
                     Cognate phage site: 186_attP."
